KISSNER


Kissner is a major salt and packaged ice melter manufacturer supplying a wide range of high-quality products. Established over 130 years ago, Kissner has evolved to become a trusted market leader known for providing reliable service to an impressive list of clientele throughout North America. We have the experience and resources to be your top supplier. Kissner has worldwide vendor relationships to ensure prompt and efficient sourcing of all your chemical needs. We supply salt from multiple origin points to provide our customers with the best product to meet their specific needs. Our experienced and dedicated staff will ensure you get the product you want, when you need it and in excellent condition. Our manufacturing and distribution facilities span throughout North America and are strategically located to service your delivery needs.



KISSNER’S QUALITYKissner’s QUALITY is the result of our commitment to excellence, focused effort and intelligent product innovation. We ensure the highest quality in all of our product offerings.

THE HIGHEST STANDARDSKissner understands what it takes to achieve the highest standards and is recognized as a respected supplier.

A LEADER IN MANY INDUSTRIESKissner is a worldwide leader in the ice melters, salt, and chemical supply chains.

YOUR COMPLETE SOLUTIONOur diverse offerings provide customers with a complete ingredient supply, packaging and distribution solution.






