Insider Activity


Individual




Matthew S. Kissner



Mr. Matthew S. Kissner is Chairman at John Wiley & Sons, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at National Bankruptcy Services LLC, U.S. Retirement Partners, Inc. and Regional Plan Association For New York. Mr. Kissner was previously employed as Chairman by American Radiology Services LLC, Operating Partner by Advent International Corp., EVP & Group President-Global Enterprise Solutions by Pitney Bowes, Inc., Vice President by Citibank, Inc. (New York), President & Chief Executive Officer by EntreCap Financial LLC, and a Principal by Morgan Stanley. He received his undergraduate degree from New York University and an MBA from New York University.



